    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it is showing its age. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, but there is some minor fluid seepage under the engine bay and the brakes will likely need servicing in the next few months. The exterior paint has faded in spots and there are several visible door dings and scratches throughout the body. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear on the driver\u2019s side and some of the plastic trim has become brittle, but all essential electronics remain functional. This is a straightforward, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
