    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty! I have babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to fall in love with it. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner so happy. Swing by and check it out!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
